snippet.title: Crusader Kings III - Gameplay Teaser
snippet.description:
Watch new in-game visuals of Crusader Kings III, the upcoming sequel to one of the most beloved strategy games of the decade. Conquer new lands with your armies, your diplomacy or your guile on 01 September, 2020. PRE-ORDER NOW: https://pdxint.at/ck3website

Paradox on YouTube:

Trailers, Feature Breakdowns, Dev Diaries, and more.

Gameplay of our video games, convention coverage, and other fun things from Paradox!

Paradox Grand Strategy - http://youtube.com/ParadoxGrandStrategy
Gameplay of our Grand Strategy Games. CK2, EU4, HOI4, Stellaris, and Imperator.
